Dialogue: 0,0:00:14.11,0:00:19.44,songM,,0000,0000,0000,,Piercing through the Macro sky,
Dialogue: 0,0:00:19.81,0:00:25.26,songM,,0000,0000,0000,,a thunderbolt strikes the Earth
Dialogue: 0,0:00:25.54,0:00:31.01,songM,,0000,0000,0000,,To awaken us, the young mankind,
Dialogue: 0,0:00:31.22,0:00:37.21,songM,,0000,0000,0000,,the Light struck
Dialogue: 0,0:00:37.53,0:00:43.28,songM,,0000,0000,0000,,Macross! Macross!
Dialogue: 0,0:00:43.55,0:00:49.02,songM,,0000,0000,0000,,The brave youths who arise
Dialogue: 0,0:00:49.28,0:00:53.13,songM,,0000,0000,0000,,and fight to protect their loved ones
Dialogue: 0,0:00:53.42,0:00:58.23,songM,,0000,0000,0000,,Will set out on their journey\Nas the war rages on.
Dialogue: 0,0:00:58.50,0:01:01.49,songM,,0000,0000,0000,,Will you love me tomorrow?
Dialogue: 0,0:01:01.73,0:01:06.86,songM,,0000,0000,0000,,Slicing through the darkness they fly toward
Dialogue: 0,0:01:07.18,0:01:12.88,songM,,0000,0000,0000,,That blue planet that shines in the distance
Dialogue: 0,0:01:13.16,0:01:18.37,songM,,0000,0000,0000,,Macross! Macross!
Dialogue: 0,0:01:20.20,0:01:24.50,songM,,0000,0000,0000,,Macross!
Dialogue: 0,0:01:39.61,0:01:43.29,narration,,0000,0000,0000,,Captain Global ordered the Macross to\Nfly low as an intimidation tactic
Dialogue: 0,0:01:43.29,0:01:46.26,narration,,0000,0000,0000,,to drop off the 56,000\Ncivilians currently on board.
Dialogue: 0,0:01:46.41,0:01:50.74,narration,,0000,0000,0000,,However, a Zentradi attack caused the\NMacross's barrier to explode,
Dialogue: 0,0:01:50.81,0:01:55.16,narration,,0000,0000,0000,,destroying not only the enemy fleet\Nbut a city on the Earth's surface.
Dialogue: 0,0:01:55.28,0:01:58.58,narration,,0000,0000,0000,,The Macross is now in a more\Npainful position than ever.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:00.11,0:02:06.13,signM,,0000,0000,0000,,{\pos(88,141)}PARADISE LOST
Dialogue: 0,0:02:06.23,0:02:11.11,narration,,0000,0000,0000,,Meanwhile, in the Zentradi main fleet,\Nnew developments are in motion.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:13.07,0:02:14.75,Macross1,,0000,0000,0000,,I can't believe it.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:15.40,0:02:17.12,Macross1,,0000,0000,0000,,Show me those visuals again.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:25.34,0:02:33.20,Macross1,,0000,0000,0000,,According to our reports, there is disorder\Namong those dispatched to Earth.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:33.54,0:02:36.66,Macross1,,0000,0000,0000,,And the miclones seem to have developed\Nyet another new weapon.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:37.49,0:02:39.99,Macross1,,0000,0000,0000,,Facing them would prove rather difficult.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:40.12,0:02:42.47,Macross1,,0000,0000,0000,,In any case, you said I had new orders?
Dialogue: 0,0:02:43.60,0:02:47.83,Macross1,,0000,0000,0000,,Return to the Earth.\NThis will require someone with experience.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:48.26,0:02:50.98,Macross1,,0000,0000,0000,,I'll have them refrain from further\Noperations until your arrival.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:51.02,0:02:52.03,Macross1,,0000,0000,0000,,Excellency?
Dialogue: 0,0:02:52.35,0:02:53.55,Macross1,,0000,0000,0000,,What is it?
Dialogue: 0,0:02:54.16,0:02:58.02,Macross1,,0000,0000,0000,,Could you place the Adoclas Fleet\Nunder my command?
Dialogue: 0,0:02:58.09,0:02:59.52,Macross1,,0000,0000,0000,,You think that will be necessary?
Dialogue: 0,0:03:00.02,0:03:03.97,Macross1,,0000,0000,0000,,In the short term, I would like to be\Nprepared for any contingency.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:06.02,0:03:07.44,Macross1,,0000,0000,0000,,Very well, you have my permission.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:07.81,0:03:08.61,Macross1,,0000,0000,0000,,Sir!
Dialogue: 0,0:03:10.20,0:03:12.22,Macross1,,0000,0000,0000,,Commander Britai of the Adoclas Fleet...
Dialogue: 0,0:03:12.97,0:03:14.00,Macross1,,0000,0000,0000,,Was there something else?
Dialogue: 0,0:03:14.16,0:03:17.02,Macross1,,0000,0000,0000,,Your speech has become impolite.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:17.73,0:03:19.61,Macross1,,0000,0000,0000,,Your Excellency must be imagining it.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:33.07,0:03:34.03,Macross1,,0000,0000,0000,,How did it go, sir?
Dialogue: 0,0:03:34.12,0:03:36.65,Macross1,,0000,0000,0000,,I'm taking the Adoclas Fleet and\Nreturning to that star system.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:37.41,0:03:38.18,Macross1,,0000,0000,0000,,Aah...
Dialogue: 0,0:03:38.56,0:03:40.60,Macross1,,0000,0000,0000,,With a fleet of 1,200 ships.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:40.68,0:03:44.57,Macross1,,0000,0000,0000,,Yes, I think I understand exactly\Nwhat his Excellency Bodolzaa intends.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:05.01,0:04:07.44,Macross1,,0000,0000,0000,,Still, 1,200 ships might not be enough.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:08.46,0:04:09.87,Macross1,,0000,0000,0000,,I see...
Dialogue: 0,0:04:22.83,0:04:25.73,Macross1,,0000,0000,0000,,All ships, prepare to fold\Nto operation space!
Dialogue: 0,0:04:26.24,0:04:27.83,Macross1,,0000,0000,0000,,All ships, prepare for fold!
Dialogue: 0,0:04:28.02,0:04:30.00,Macross1,,0000,0000,0000,,Sync coordinate patterns with the flagship!
Dialogue: 0,0:04:30.54,0:04:32.20,Macross1,,0000,0000,0000,,Move into fold position!
Dialogue: 0,0:04:32.64,0:04:34.43,Macross1,,0000,0000,0000,,Commencing fold countdown!
Dialogue: 0,0:04:58.72,0:04:59.89,Macross1,,0000,0000,0000,,Okay!
Dialogue: 0,0:05:00.46,0:05:01.35,Macross1,,0000,0000,0000,,Okay!
Dialogue: 0,0:05:04.80,0:05:06.33,Macross1,,0000,0000,0000,,There sure are a lot of trucks coming in.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:08.35,0:05:10.32,Macross1,,0000,0000,0000,,Maybe we'll be heading out someplace again.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:10.91,0:05:13.40,Macross1,,0000,0000,0000,,They say that everyone thinks we're dead.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:14.09,0:05:17.35,Macross1,,0000,0000,0000,,What, so now we're ghosts without\Na country to call home?
Dialogue: 0,0:05:18.00,0:05:20.99,Macross1,,0000,0000,0000,,What's so bad about that?\NWe're already used to living here.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:21.05,0:05:22.42,Macross1,,0000,0000,0000,,I guess we're "Macrossians," huh?
Dialogue: 0,0:05:24.85,0:05:27.40,songM,,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}Zero-g love, zero-g love!
Dialogue: 0,0:05:27.93,0:05:30.53,songM,,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}Zero-g love, zero-g love!
Dialogue: 0,0:05:29.18,0:05:31.54,Macross1,,0000,0000,0000,,Dear Kenichi and Yoshimi Kakizaki...
Dialogue: 0,0:05:31.34,0:05:36.84,songM,,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}With him after school, on my way home
Dialogue: 0,0:05:32.15,0:05:34.02,Macross1,,0000,0000,0000,,While in action above the\NOntario Autonomous Region,
Dialogue: 0,0:05:34.69,0:05:38.16,Macross1,,0000,0000,0000,,your son, 2nd Lieutenant Hayao Kakizaki, was...
Dialogue: 0,0:05:37.51,0:05:43.29,songM,,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}At the corner of that same old intersection
Dialogue: 0,0:05:43.89,0:05:48.01,songM,,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}He made sure no one else was...
Dialogue: 0,0:06:13.54,0:06:14.52,Macross1,,0000,0000,0000,,Leader!
Dialogue: 0,0:06:16.00,0:06:17.37,Macross1,,0000,0000,0000,,Let's get out of here for a bit.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:18.00,0:06:19.21,Macross1,,0000,0000,0000,,What were you doing, Leader?
Dialogue: 0,0:06:19.47,0:06:20.80,Macross1,,0000,0000,0000,,Quit calling me Leader!
Dialogue: 0,0:06:21.28,0:06:23.38,Macross1,,0000,0000,0000,,I was writing a death notification\Nletter to Kakizaki's parents.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:28.89,0:06:31.42,Macross1,,0000,0000,0000,,I just received a special promotion to 2nd Lt.\Nless than a month ago.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:31.74,0:06:35.00,Macross1,,0000,0000,0000,,So why am I now being promoted to\N1st Lt. and given my own team?
Dialogue: 0,0:06:36.07,0:06:39.08,Macross1,,0000,0000,0000,,Well, they made me a squadron\Ncommander, didn't they?
Dialogue: 0,0:06:39.81,0:06:43.42,Macross1,,0000,0000,0000,,Pretty much all those replacement\Npilots the military sent us
Dialogue: 0,0:06:44.21,0:06:46.23,Macross1,,0000,0000,0000,,are even greener than we are.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:47.83,0:06:50.02,Macross1,,0000,0000,0000,,But I don't have any experience\Ncommanding a team.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:50.15,0:06:51.49,Macross1,,0000,0000,0000,,You'll do fine, Max.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:53.81,0:06:55.99,Macross1,,0000,0000,0000,,It looks like they've finished\Nloading the supplies.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:59.55,0:07:01.89,Macross1,,0000,0000,0000,,That's a UN Forces\Nofficer's transport, isn't it?
Dialogue: 0,0:07:05.74,0:07:06.81,Macross1,,0000,0000,0000,,What the heck is going on?
Dialogue: 0,0:07:10.57,0:07:12.31,Macross1,,0000,0000,0000,,Looks like top brass, huh?
Dialogue: 0,0:07:15.17,0:07:17.08,Macross1,,0000,0000,0000,,Is what they've been saying true?
Dialogue: 0,0:07:17.58,0:07:20.01,Macross1,,0000,0000,0000,,What, that they might make us leave the Earth?
Dialogue: 0,0:07:21.92,0:07:25.08,Macross1,,0000,0000,0000,,And after all we went\Nthrough to get back here.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:25.69,0:07:27.54,Macross1,,0000,0000,0000,,This might be the last sunset we see.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:46.86,0:07:48.54,Macross1,,0000,0000,0000,,Hey, dinner's ready!
Dialogue: 0,0:07:48.96,0:07:49.89,Macross1,,0000,0000,0000,,What is it today?
Dialogue: 0,0:07:51.56,0:07:52.67,Macross1,,0000,0000,0000,,Beef stew.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:53.45,0:07:54.73,Macross1,,0000,0000,0000,,All right!
Dialogue: 0,0:07:56.90,0:08:01.43,songM,,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}On the cafe terrace, dyed crimson with the sunset,
Dialogue: 0,0:07:57.95,0:07:59.80,Macross1,,0000,0000,0000,,Ah! A Lynn Minmay song!
Dialogue: 0,0:07:59.97,0:08:01.43,Macross1,,0000,0000,0000,,Those are always nice to hear.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:01.70,0:08:05.79,songM,,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}The fragrance of Turkish coffee fills the air
Dialogue: 0,0:08:04.28,0:08:05.29,Macross1,,0000,0000,0000,,Done... Ow!
Dialogue: 0,0:08:06.38,0:08:10.98,songM,,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}Along with a listless tango rhythm.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:07.34,0:08:09.33,Macross1,,0000,0000,0000,,And today's coffee is Blue Mountain Blend!
Dialogue: 0,0:08:09.74,0:08:10.67,Macross1,,0000,0000,0000,,Yes!
Dialogue: 0,0:08:11.35,0:08:15.03,songM,,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}I'm alone and lonely, but if I dance
Dialogue: 0,0:08:11.34,0:08:13.01,Macross1,,0000,0000,0000,,Tonight's dinner sure has a lot of meat!
Dialogue: 0,0:08:13.56,0:08:15.29,Macross1,,0000,0000,0000,,I tell you, my cooking's gotten pretty good!
Dialogue: 0,0:08:15.09,0:08:19.99,songM,,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}A breeze will blow through my heart.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:17.20,0:08:20.36,Macross1,,0000,0000,0000,,It sure is nice to listen to Minmay while eating!
Dialogue: 0,0:08:20.52,0:08:23.78,songM,,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}If you don't show up,
Dialogue: 0,0:08:23.79,0:08:24.55,Macross1,,0000,0000,0000,,By the way...
Dialogue: 0,0:08:24.78,0:08:29.00,songM,,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}I wonder who I'll be dancing with tonight?
Dialogue: 0,0:08:29.46,0:08:31.38,songM,,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}Silver Moon
Dialogue: 0,0:08:31.77,0:08:33.89,songM,,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}Red Moon
Dialogue: 0,0:08:34.17,0:08:38.44,songM,,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}You're so cold, Shanghai dandy
Dialogue: 0,0:08:34.17,0:08:37.88,Macross1,,0000,0000,0000,,By the way, do you think we can make\Nit back in that beat-up Reguld?
Dialogue: 0,0:08:38.64,0:08:40.57,Macross1,,0000,0000,0000,,We'll fly it by splitting up\Npiloting duties in the cockpit.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:38.97,0:08:43.45,songM,,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}The smoke from the Gitanes gets in my eyes
Dialogue: 0,0:08:41.00,0:08:42.14,Macross1,,0000,0000,0000,,Everything's all ready.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:43.18,0:08:44.13,Macross1,,0000,0000,0000,,Oh...
Dialogue: 0,0:08:44.91,0:08:46.97,Macross1,,0000,0000,0000,,All that's left is to wait for the signal, huh?
Dialogue: 0,0:08:48.52,0:08:50.14,Macross1,,0000,0000,0000,,That disco sure was fun.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:51.04,0:08:51.99,Macross1,,0000,0000,0000,,Disco...
Dialogue: 0,0:08:52.15,0:08:55.00,Macross1,,0000,0000,0000,,Minmay's not bad, but that\NKim is really cute!
Dialogue: 0,0:08:55.52,0:08:59.01,Macross1,,0000,0000,0000,,Give me Shammy any day!\NThat "No {\i1}waaay!{\i0}" of hers!
Dialogue: 0,0:09:02.06,0:09:06.24,songM,,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}The night makes the gypsy violin cry,
Dialogue: 0,0:09:03.78,0:09:06.95,Macross1,,0000,0000,0000,,I'll probably never see Vanessa again.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:06.58,0:09:10.81,songM,,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}The wine bottle and the two glasses,
Dialogue: 0,0:09:11.00,0:09:12.37,songM,,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}I burn for...
Dialogue: 0,0:09:14.30,0:09:15.66,Macross1,,0000,0000,0000,,Captain, if you'll excuse me.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:38.46,0:09:44.88,narration,,0000,0000,0000,,"Earth UN Forces High Command orders this\Nvessel and the civilians under its protection"
Dialogue: 0,0:09:45.05,0:09:50.43,narration,,0000,0000,0000,,"to depart Earth space within 24 hours\Nof receipt of this document."
Dialogue: 0,0:09:50.57,0:09:54.09,narration,,0000,0000,0000,,"Should this order not be carried out,\Nthe use of force is..."
Dialogue: 0,0:09:58.77,0:10:00.19,Macross1,,0000,0000,0000,,Captain Global...
Dialogue: 0,0:10:00.66,0:10:05.79,Macross1,,0000,0000,0000,,Captain Hayase, as expected, we've\Nbeen ordered to leave the Earth.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:36.10,0:10:39.07,Macross1,,0000,0000,0000,,I was prepared for the worst,
Dialogue: 0,0:10:39.79,0:10:44.32,Macross1,,0000,0000,0000,,but for them to involve these\N56,000 innocent civilians is just...
Dialogue: 0,0:10:46.14,0:10:47.34,Macross1,,0000,0000,0000,,I agree.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:48.29,0:10:50.32,Macross1,,0000,0000,0000,,Contact the television station.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:50.78,0:10:51.58,Macross1,,0000,0000,0000,,Yes, sir.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:57.65,0:10:58.54,Macross1,,0000,0000,0000,,Bridge here.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:59.38,0:11:01.34,Macross1,,0000,0000,0000,,This is Global.\NAre all the supplies loaded?
Dialogue: 0,0:11:02.00,0:11:03.20,Macross1,,0000,0000,0000,,Yes, the loading is complete.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:06.72,0:11:09.09,Macross1,,0000,0000,0000,,Claudia, prepare for launch.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:10.33,0:11:11.55,Macross1,,0000,0000,0000,,Prepare for launch!
Dialogue: 0,0:11:12.25,0:11:13.60,Macross1,,0000,0000,0000,,Yes, sir!
Dialogue: 0,0:11:14.50,0:11:15.60,Macross1,,0000,0000,0000,,Prepare for launch!
Dialogue: 0,0:11:16.32,0:11:18.59,Macross1,,0000,0000,0000,,So the rumors were true after all.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:19.36,0:11:23.01,Macross1,,0000,0000,0000,,Well, we did wipe out an entire city.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:23.27,0:11:25.58,Macross1,,0000,0000,0000,,But that couldn't be helped!
Dialogue: 0,0:11:25.87,0:11:27.75,Macross1,,0000,0000,0000,,The real problem is the civilians.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:27.97,0:11:30.12,Macross1,,0000,0000,0000,,Not only does the world already\Nthink they're dead,
Dialogue: 0,0:11:30.37,0:11:32.98,Macross1,,0000,0000,0000,,but now that all this has happened,\Nno one would even take them in.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:33.26,0:11:35.11,Macross1,,0000,0000,0000,,Hurry up with those final section checks.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:37.34,0:11:40.42,Macross1,,0000,0000,0000,,Hey, Capt. Hayase's father is\Ntop brass at High Command, right?
Dialogue: 0,0:11:40.47,0:11:41.36,Macross1,,0000,0000,0000,,Why can't...
Dialogue: 0,0:11:40.69,0:11:41.40,Macross1,,0000,0000,0000,,{\c&HFFFFFF&}Shammy!
Dialogue: 0,0:11:42.69,0:11:44.43,Macross1,,0000,0000,0000,,If you mention this to Misa,\Nyou're on your own.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:44.79,0:11:45.77,Macross1,,0000,0000,0000,,Now hurry up with those checks!
Dialogue: 0,0:11:45.87,0:11:46.89,Macross1,,0000,0000,0000,,Yes, ma'am!
Dialogue: 0,0:12:01.90,0:12:03.02,Macross1,,0000,0000,0000,,Signal, mark!
Dialogue: 0,0:12:03.54,0:12:05.01,Macross1,,0000,0000,0000,,Engines activated!
Dialogue: 0,0:12:05.40,0:12:06.51,Macross1,,0000,0000,0000,,Launch!
Dialogue: 0,0:12:21.45,0:12:22.63,Macross1,,0000,0000,0000,,Here goes!
Dialogue: 0,0:12:59.02,0:13:00.51,Macross1,,0000,0000,0000,,Radar room to the bridge.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:00.66,0:13:02.79,Macross1,,0000,0000,0000,,Gravitational waves detected\Non the dark side of the Moon.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:03.74,0:13:05.79,Macross1,,0000,0000,0000,,They could be fold echoes.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:09.50,0:13:11.80,Macross1,,0000,0000,0000,,Captain! We've detected gravity waves\Nin the direction of the Moon!
Dialogue: 0,0:13:12.11,0:13:12.83,Macross1,,0000,0000,0000,,A fold?
Dialogue: 0,0:13:12.91,0:13:13.40,Macross1,,0000,0000,0000,,Yes, sir.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:13.48,0:13:14.73,Macross1,,0000,0000,0000,,Put it on the monitor.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:19.31,0:13:20.66,Macross1,,0000,0000,0000,,Calculate the number of ships.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:20.73,0:13:21.67,Macross1,,0000,0000,0000,,Yes, sir.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:22.09,0:13:24.60,Macross1,,0000,0000,0000,,No way!\NMore enemy ships?
Dialogue: 0,0:13:26.39,0:13:27.36,Macross1,,0000,0000,0000,,I'm sorry.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:30.72,0:13:33.43,Macross1,,0000,0000,0000,,An unidentified object is above the\Nship and ascending rapidly!
Dialogue: 0,0:13:34.92,0:13:37.12,Macross1,,0000,0000,0000,,Did we launch any planes from the Macross?
Dialogue: 0,0:13:37.18,0:13:37.74,Macross1,,0000,0000,0000,,No, sir.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:38.04,0:13:40.75,Macross1,,0000,0000,0000,,Another unidentified object has dropped out of\Nthe atmosphere and is descending rapidly.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:41.04,0:13:43.09,Macross1,,0000,0000,0000,,It's rendezvousing with the first object.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:47.45,0:13:49.65,Macross1,,0000,0000,0000,,Valkyrie squadrons, go to B-mode!
Dialogue: 0,0:13:50.24,0:13:53.27,Macross1,,0000,0000,0000,,I'm detecting more gravity waves.\NThere are more than earlier.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:54.29,0:13:58.03,Macross1,,0000,0000,0000,,Based on these readings, this makes\Na total of at least 1,000 ships.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:00.87,0:14:03.96,Macross1,,0000,0000,0000,,We're just one ship. That's not going to change\Nno matter how many ships they send.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:04.15,0:14:06.07,Macross1,,0000,0000,0000,,Huh? No way!
Dialogue: 0,0:14:05.58,0:14:08.18,Macross1,,0000,0000,0000,,{\c&HFFFFFF&}But they've never sent 1,000 ships before!
Dialogue: 0,0:14:08.63,0:14:10.65,Macross1,,0000,0000,0000,,That's enough!\NDon't you have any guts?
Dialogue: 0,0:14:11.44,0:14:13.59,Macross1,,0000,0000,0000,,High Command must have\npicked them up as well.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:14.01,0:14:15.18,Macross1,,0000,0000,0000,,Have they contacted us?
Dialogue: 0,0:14:15.31,0:14:16.61,Macross1,,0000,0000,0000,,Not so far.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:16.99,0:14:19.07,Macross1,,0000,0000,0000,,So they've washed their hands of us.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:19.55,0:14:20.54,Macross1,,0000,0000,0000,,But why?!
Dialogue: 0,0:14:22.94,0:14:26.00,Macross1,,0000,0000,0000,,They probably think that if the\NMacross is destroyed,
Dialogue: 0,0:14:26.71,0:14:29.97,Macross1,,0000,0000,0000,,they can use it as an opportunity\Nto open negotiations.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:45.75,0:14:47.49,Macross1,,0000,0000,0000,,We've finally returned...
Dialogue: 0,0:14:48.92,0:14:50.44,Macross1,,0000,0000,0000,,Returned?
Dialogue: 0,0:14:51.47,0:14:53.91,Macross1,,0000,0000,0000,,I've patched through to Fleet\NCommander Lap'Lamiz.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:56.38,0:14:58.98,Macross1,,0000,0000,0000,,Well done, I will take over from here.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:59.38,0:15:04.30,Macross1,,0000,0000,0000,,You've brought quite a fleet to deal\Nwith a single miclone vessel.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:08.24,0:15:10.75,Macross1,,0000,0000,0000,,That little ship has a way of burning\Nthose who get near it.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:10.80,0:15:12.29,Macross1,,0000,0000,0000,,That incident with Milia, for example.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:12.62,0:15:15.28,Macross1,,0000,0000,0000,,Hold your tongue!\NLet's see how much better you do!
Dialogue: 0,0:15:15.79,0:15:18.29,Macross1,,0000,0000,0000,,Do? For the moment,\NI'm doing nothing at all.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:18.58,0:15:19.48,Macross1,,0000,0000,0000,,Excellency...
Dialogue: 0,0:15:19.69,0:15:21.24,Macross1,,0000,0000,0000,,If you'll excuse me, something\Nseems to have come up.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:21.79,0:15:23.75,Macross1,,0000,0000,0000,,What are you scheming, Britai?
Dialogue: 0,0:15:23.94,0:15:25.52,Macross1,,0000,0000,0000,,We'll see, won't we?
Dialogue: 0,0:15:28.75,0:15:31.04,Macross1,,0000,0000,0000,,The three have been returned\Nto their normal size.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:53.03,0:15:54.32,Macross1,,0000,0000,0000,,Let's hear your report.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:54.72,0:15:55.81,Macross1,,0000,0000,0000,,Yes, sir!
Dialogue: 0,0:15:57.11,0:16:01.52,narration,,0000,0000,0000,,Fighting to speak first, the three began to\Ndescribe their experiences aboard the Macross.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:02.85,0:16:07.03,Macross1,,0000,0000,0000,,The items here are just the smallest part of\Ntheir "culture," or whatever it's called.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:07.34,0:16:09.33,Macross1,,0000,0000,0000,,There were people there who\Nweren't even soldiers!
Dialogue: 0,0:16:10.31,0:16:14.12,Macross1,,0000,0000,0000,,This is called a "television" and\Nis used for entertainment.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:14.54,0:16:16.07,Macross1,,0000,0000,0000,,Speaking of entertainment,
Dialogue: 0,0:16:16.07,0:16:18.16,Macross1,,0000,0000,0000,,sometimes whole crowds will gather to\Nwatch a single person for enjoyment.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:19.45,0:16:21.99,Macross1,,0000,0000,0000,,They have done an excellent job of\Nreconstructing the ship's interior.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:22.33,0:16:26.03,Macross1,,0000,0000,0000,,However, they've also made additions\Nthat we could not understand.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:29.39,0:16:32.62,Macross1,,0000,0000,0000,,They have places where many of them\Nwill gather together.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:33.62,0:16:36.31,Macross1,,0000,0000,0000,,The people move around freely there.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:37.68,0:16:41.51,Macross1,,0000,0000,0000,,What's more, men and women\Nare in constant contact!
Dialogue: 0,0:16:44.06,0:16:46.43,Macross1,,0000,0000,0000,,And it's not dangerous at all.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:48.89,0:16:50.87,Macross1,,0000,0000,0000,,On the contrary, it feels good!
Dialogue: 0,0:16:54.12,0:16:56.78,narration,,0000,0000,0000,,Like a spring, the three agents'\Nreport flowed forth,
Dialogue: 0,0:16:57.09,0:17:01.26,narration,,0000,0000,0000,,and Britai and Exsedol could only\Nlisten in astonishment.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:01.61,0:17:03.72,Macross1,,0000,0000,0000,,All right, enough!\NThere's no end to this.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:06.09,0:17:06.98,Macross1,,0000,0000,0000,,Well?
Dialogue: 0,0:17:07.18,0:17:09.61,Macross1,,0000,0000,0000,,Sir, I am now interested in\Ngoing to see for myself.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:09.78,0:17:11.64,Macross1,,0000,0000,0000,,This is most intriguing, wouldn't you say?
Dialogue: 0,0:17:11.98,0:17:15.60,Macross1,,0000,0000,0000,,Having you go would present difficulties,\Nand right now I must send my report.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:16.08,0:17:18.63,Macross1,,0000,0000,0000,,Prepare your report at once.\NYou may go.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:19.00,0:17:20.06,Macross1,,0000,0000,0000,,Yes, sir!
Dialogue: 0,0:17:27.12,0:17:29.63,Macross1,,0000,0000,0000,,Did you guys really hand in everything?
Dialogue: 0,0:17:29.95,0:17:30.93,Macross1,,0000,0000,0000,,And what about you?
Dialogue: 0,0:17:31.02,0:17:33.45,Macross1,,0000,0000,0000,,Huh? So we all secretly kept some things?
Dialogue: 0,0:17:33.53,0:17:34.59,Macross1,,0000,0000,0000,,Okay, let's take a look.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:41.47,0:17:44.00,Macross1,,0000,0000,0000,,A television... and a "player," right?
Dialogue: 0,0:17:44.11,0:17:46.90,Macross1,,0000,0000,0000,,And a Minmay holo-disc!
Dialogue: 0,0:17:47.60,0:17:50.00,Macross1,,0000,0000,0000,,I can't believe you hid something like that!
Dialogue: 0,0:17:50.11,0:17:51.41,Macross1,,0000,0000,0000,,You're one to talk.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:51.43,0:17:53.43,Macross1,,0000,0000,0000,,I kept a Minmay doll.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:53.48,0:17:54.49,Macross1,,0000,0000,0000,,What do we do with this?
Dialogue: 0,0:17:54.54,0:17:56.51,Macross1,,0000,0000,0000,,I really wanna show some of the other guys.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:56.90,0:17:59.06,Macross1,,0000,0000,0000,,If we're not careful,\Nwe could be put to death!
Dialogue: 0,0:18:04.02,0:18:06.00,Macross1,,0000,0000,0000,,Try this!\NGo on!
Dialogue: 0,0:18:12.95,0:18:14.09,Macross1,,0000,0000,0000,,This is great!
Dialogue: 0,0:18:15.25,0:18:16.55,Macross1,,0000,0000,0000,,I've never tasted something like this!
Dialogue: 0,0:18:16.78,0:18:19.35,Macross1,,0000,0000,0000,,Listen up, they call this stuff "candy"!
Dialogue: 0,0:18:19.52,0:18:21.53,Macross1,,0000,0000,0000,,Amazing! I've never come across\Nanything like it!
Dialogue: 0,0:18:21.60,0:18:24.47,songM,,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}Whoosh, whoosh! Whoosh, whoosh!
Dialogue: 0,0:18:24.76,0:18:28.99,songM,,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}My boyfriend is a pilot
Dialogue: 0,0:18:30.03,0:18:31.53,songM,,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}Shining, making a...
Dialogue: 0,0:18:33.03,0:18:34.64,Macross1,,0000,0000,0000,,This is called a "song."
Dialogue: 0,0:18:34.76,0:18:36.59,songM,,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}...sudden climb
Dialogue: 0,0:18:36.97,0:18:42.31,songM,,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}Leaving a long trail of vapor
Dialogue: 0,0:18:37.83,0:18:39.33,Macross1,,0000,0000,0000,,There's something strange about it.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:42.82,0:18:48.57,songM,,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}He traces two big hearts
Dialogue: 0,0:18:48.98,0:18:51.04,narration,,0000,0000,0000,,The souvenirs that the three\Nhad brought back
Dialogue: 0,0:18:49.42,0:18:55.97,songM,,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}A love sign in the big, blue sky
Dialogue: 0,0:18:51.29,0:18:55.35,narration,,0000,0000,0000,,were met with admiring eyes,\Nand in no time at all,
Dialogue: 0,0:18:55.65,0:18:58.03,narration,,0000,0000,0000,,word had spread among the\Nlower-ranking officers.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:56.34,0:18:58.15,songM,,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}"I love you, you..."
Dialogue: 0,0:19:24.11,0:19:27.00,Macross1,,0000,0000,0000,,Crew of the Macross and\Neveryone else aboard,
Dialogue: 0,0:19:27.38,0:19:29.52,Macross1,,0000,0000,0000,,I must now inform you of\Nan important decision.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:31.05,0:19:32.87,Macross1,,0000,0000,0000,,Since returning to Earth,
Dialogue: 0,0:19:33.01,0:19:38.53,Macross1,,0000,0000,0000,,I have repeatedly asked both the Earth\NUN Government and the UN Forces
Dialogue: 0,0:19:38.54,0:19:42.46,Macross1,,0000,0000,0000,,for authorization to let our citizens disembark,\Nbut the response has not been favorable.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:42.82,0:19:43.82,Macross1,,0000,0000,0000,,What the heck?!
Dialogue: 0,0:19:43.99,0:19:46.20,Macross1,,0000,0000,0000,,I will be frank:
Dialogue: 0,0:19:48.93,0:19:54.06,Macross1,,0000,0000,0000,,UN Forces High Command has ordered\Nthe Macross to leave Earth.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:53.48,0:19:54.81,Macross1,,0000,0000,0000,, {\b1\c&HFFFFFF&}That's crazy!
Dialogue: 0,0:19:54.96,0:19:57.27,Macross1,,0000,0000,0000,,What's going to happen to us?
Dialogue: 0,0:20:00.33,0:20:05.07,Macross1,,0000,0000,0000,,They said that if we do not\Ncomply within 24 hours,
Dialogue: 0,0:20:05.43,0:20:07.73,Macross1,,0000,0000,0000,,UN Military forces will attack this vessel.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:07.94,0:20:08.77,Macross1,,0000,0000,0000,,Huh?
Dialogue: 0,0:20:08.90,0:20:09.83,Macross1,,0000,0000,0000,,That's impossible!
Dialogue: 0,0:20:09.91,0:20:11.87,Macross1,,0000,0000,0000,,The Earth's turned it's back on us!
Dialogue: 0,0:20:12.63,0:20:15.72,Macross1,,0000,0000,0000,,We could never fight against the Earth.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:15.89,0:20:19.85,Macross1,,0000,0000,0000,,The Macross is finished taking in supplies and\Nprepared for immediate launch.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:20.95,0:20:23.80,Macross1,,0000,0000,0000,,Now more than ever, I would\Nlike to ask for your help.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:24.38,0:20:27.89,Macross1,,0000,0000,0000,,Wait for the day when the Earth\Nwill take us back.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:27.92,0:20:29.98,Macross1,,0000,0000,0000,,If that day comes...
Dialogue: 0,0:20:30.55,0:20:32.86,Macross1,,0000,0000,0000,,No, that day will surely come,
Dialogue: 0,0:20:33.09,0:20:35.38,Macross1,,0000,0000,0000,,and until it does, we will do\Nour utmost to survive.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:35.78,0:20:37.52,Macross1,,0000,0000,0000,,I don't know how...
Dialogue: 0,0:20:39.87,0:20:43.01,Macross1,,0000,0000,0000,,How I can apologize to you, our citizens?
Dialogue: 0,0:20:48.84,0:20:52.46,Macross1,,0000,0000,0000,,Everyone, I don't know much about\Ngovernments or armies,
Dialogue: 0,0:20:53.36,0:20:56.45,Macross1,,0000,0000,0000,,but this is where we've lived\Nfor a long, long time.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:57.15,0:20:59.45,Macross1,,0000,0000,0000,,We're all in this together, right?
Dialogue: 0,0:20:59.59,0:21:02.02,Macross1,,0000,0000,0000,,Besides, our city is here,\Ninside the Macross.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:03.82,0:21:08.05,Macross1,,0000,0000,0000,,We've made it through so much already,\Nso I know we'll make it through this!
Dialogue: 0,0:21:08.45,0:21:11.85,Macross1,,0000,0000,0000,,Everyone on the Macross is like family.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:12.37,0:21:15.80,Macross1,,0000,0000,0000,,The captain and the others are\Nall doing their best for us.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:19.28,0:21:23.27,Macross1,,0000,0000,0000,,I know that one day we'll be able to come back.\NThere's always hope.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:23.74,0:21:24.59,narration,,0000,0000,0000,,Minmay...
Dialogue: 0,0:21:25.66,0:21:30.33,Macross1,,0000,0000,0000,,So until then... everyone,\Nuntil then, the Macross...
Dialogue: 0,0:21:31.45,0:21:35.05,Macross1,,0000,0000,0000,,The Macross is our home.\NIt's our homeland.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:35.25,0:21:37.49,Macross1,,0000,0000,0000,,Minmay knows just what to say!
Dialogue: 0,0:21:37.94,0:21:42.14,Macross1,,0000,0000,0000,,Now it's up to us! We hafta work together\Nso the Macross can come back!
Dialogue: 0,0:21:42.42,0:21:43.61,Macross1,,0000,0000,0000,,That's right!
Dialogue: 0,0:21:43.70,0:21:44.78,Macross1,,0000,0000,0000,,Let's do it!
Dialogue: 0,0:21:45.10,0:21:47.01,Macross1,,0000,0000,0000,,All right!
Dialogue: 0,0:21:48.63,0:21:50.30,Macross1,,0000,0000,0000,,Macross, stand by for launch!
Dialogue: 0,0:21:50.33,0:21:51.46,Macross1,,0000,0000,0000,,Get to your stations!
Dialogue: 0,0:21:51.67,0:21:53.93,Macross1,,0000,0000,0000,,Main control systems are all green.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:54.00,0:21:54.99,Macross1,,0000,0000,0000,,Launch alert!
Dialogue: 0,0:21:55.07,0:21:57.92,Macross1,,0000,0000,0000,,Gravity-control levels are rising.\NCommencing liftoff.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:58.39,0:22:00.02,Macross1,,0000,0000,0000,,Level is minus 0.2.
Dialogue: 0,0:22:07.71,0:22:08.99,Macross1,,0000,0000,0000,,All sections are in the clear.
Dialogue: 0,0:22:09.83,0:22:11.51,Macross1,,0000,0000,0000,,Activating reaction propulsion drive.
Dialogue: 0,0:22:12.09,0:22:13.41,Macross1,,0000,0000,0000,,Maximum propulsion!
Dialogue: 0,0:22:17.18,0:22:20.15,Macross1,,0000,0000,0000,,We're now heading out into space.
Dialogue: 0,0:22:21.88,0:22:24.51,Macross1,,0000,0000,0000,,This broadcast is also being aired on Earth.
Dialogue: 0,0:22:25.00,0:22:27.56,Macross1,,0000,0000,0000,,I'll now sing a song with all the\Nfeelings I have for the Earth.
Dialogue: 0,0:22:34.19,0:22:38.92,songM,,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}An ocean filled with stardust
Dialogue: 0,0:22:39.88,0:22:44.61,songM,,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}Reflects the warm sun back
Dialogue: 0,0:22:45.84,0:22:50.48,songM,,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}A little oasis
Dialogue: 0,0:22:50.72,0:22:57.30,songM,,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}Our home, the green earth
Dialogue: 0,0:22:57.63,0:23:02.53,songM,,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}One day, we shall return
Dialogue: 0,0:23:02.67,0:23:09.20,songM,,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}So until then, please don't change
Dialogue: 0,0:23:09.59,0:23:20.42,songM,,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}"Beautiful place in my heart"
Dialogue: 0,0:23:32.44,0:23:35.40,signM,,0000,0000,0000,,{\pos(73,109)}Next Episode
Dialogue: 0,0:23:32.44,0:23:35.40,signM,,0000,0000,0000,,{\pos(296,452)}Preview
Dialogue: 0,0:23:39.23,0:23:42.64,narration,,0000,0000,0000,,The days come and go, and Hikaru and Minmay\Ncontinue to pass each other by.
Dialogue: 0,0:23:43.63,0:23:47.83,narration,,0000,0000,0000,,The movie starring Minmay\Nand Kaifun is completed.
Dialogue: 0,0:23:48.59,0:23:53.33,narration,,0000,0000,0000,,On the day of the premiere, Hikaru looks up\Nat the screen and his heart wavers.
Dialogue: 0,0:23:54.31,0:23:57.64,narration,,0000,0000,0000,,Next time on Super Dimension\NFortress Macross:
Dialogue: 0,0:23:56.79,0:24:02.45,signM,,0000,0000,0000,,{\pos(86,147)}MICRO COSMOS
Dialogue: 0,0:23:58.12,0:23:59.99,narration,,0000,0000,0000,,"MICRO COSMOS"
Dialogue: 0,0:24:17.59,0:24:23.28,songM,,0000,0000,0000,,I won't follow it anymore
Dialogue: 0,0:24:23.52,0:24:29.89,songM,,0000,0000,0000,,The shadow you cast as you run away
Dialogue: 0,0:24:30.18,0:24:36.54,songM,,0000,0000,0000,,We all keep running until the end
Dialogue: 0,0:24:36.75,0:24:44.20,songM,,0000,0000,0000,,But we still can't see the goal
Dialogue: 0,0:24:44.56,0:24:51.00,songM,,0000,0000,0000,,What awaits us after today?
Dialogue: 0,0:24:51.29,0:24:56.78,songM,,0000,0000,0000,,What awaits us beyond tomorrow?
Dialogue: 0,0:24:57.12,0:25:04.36,songM,,0000,0000,0000,,Even now, I keep running toward
Dialogue: 0,0:25:04.71,0:25:15.50,songM,,0000,0000,0000,,The light that shines so far away
